spec_data.Name: perl-Module-Manifest
spec_data.Description:
Module::Manifest can load a MANIFEST file that comes in a Perl distribution
tarball, examine the contents, and perform some simple tasks. It can also load
the MANIFEST.SKIP file and check that.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:42:29 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parse and examine a Perl distribution MANIFEST file
